<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">快速设置</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">通过<span class="link"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#systemmenu" title="系统菜单">系统菜单</a></span>中的“快速设置”按钮，您可以快速打开或关闭可用服务，并选择蓝牙设备或 Wi-Fi 网络。</p></div>
<section id="wifi"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">Wi-Fi</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide">
<div class="media media-image floatend"><div class="inner"><img src="figures/shell-exit.png" width="250" class="media media-block" alt=""></div></div>
<p class="p">点击 <span class="gui">Wi-Fi</span> 按钮关闭或重新打开 Wi-Fi。</p>
<p class="p">此按钮显示当前连接的 Wi-Fi 网络。</p>
<p class="p">点击 <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-next-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="right"></span></span> 显示可用网络。</p>
<p class="p">选择一个网络以启动连接，或选择<span class="gui">所有网络</span>以打开 <span class="link"><a href="net-wireless.html.zh-CN" title="无线网络">Wi-Fi</a></span> 设置面板。</p>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="wired"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">有线</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">有线</span>按钮以关闭或重新打开有线网络。此按钮显示有关当前有线网络连接的信息。点击 <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-next-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="right"></span></span> 可显示更多设置。选择<span class="gui">有线设置</span>以打开<span class="link"><a href="net-wired.html.zh-CN" title="有线网络">网络</a></span>设置面板。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section id="bluetooth"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">蓝牙</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">蓝牙</span>按钮以关闭或重新打开蓝牙。此按钮显示第一个设备的名称或连接的设备数量。点击 <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-next-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="right"></span></span> 可显示已配对和已连接的蓝牙设备。选择一个设备以连接或断开连接。选择<span class="gui">蓝牙设置</span>以打开<span class="link"><a href="bluetooth.html.zh-CN" title="蓝牙">蓝牙</a></span>设置面板。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section id="power"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">电源模式</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p"><span class="gui">电源模式</span>按钮显示当前的<span class="link"><a href="power-profile.html.zh-CN" title="选择电源配置">电源模式</a></span>设置。点击按钮切换到<span class="gui">节电</span>或返回当前设置。点击 <span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-next-symbolic.svg" class="media media-inline" alt="right"></span></span> 可从所有模式中进行选择。选择<span class="gui">电源设置</span>以打开<span class="link"><a href="power.html.zh-CN" title="电源和电池">电源</a></span>设置面板。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section id="toggles"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">切换</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">其他按钮显示<span class="link"><a href="display-night-light.html.zh-CN" title="调整屏幕色温">夜灯</a></span>、<span class="gui">暗色样式</span>、<span class="link"><a href="net-wireless-airplane.html.zh-CN" title="关闭无线网络（飞行模式）">飞行模式</a></span>或<span class="gui">键盘</span>背光（如果可用）的当前状态。按下按钮可打开或关闭。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section id="background"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">后台应用</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">系统上运行的后台应用程序的数量显示在系统菜单的底部。点击以显示这些应用的列表。从列表中选择一个应用程序会为该应用程序打开一个窗口，并将其从<span class="gui">后台应用</span>中删除。选择<span class="gui">应用设置</span>以打开<span class="gui">应用</span>设置面板。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section class="links" role="navigation"><div class="inner">
